weeks_detail.summary: AI field creation: build fields directly from AI query (on-the-fly aggregates, derivative dimensions). AI MCP v0: Blobby in Goose and generic AI functions - data accessible from any chat service. Streaming AI results: Blobby tells you what it's doing while doing it. Level of detail calculations: escape or force grouping independent of the rest of the query (dynamic percent of totals, comparison to unfiltered data). Dashboard tile sizing improvements. Force expose long filter lists beyond default single line. Aggregate directly from visualization when data isn't at right grain.

AI Mode launch (finishing touches, linking to workbook pages). Early Slack experience for Blobby. Training inside topic with example queries. Embed navigation custom experience and custom filters outside iframe. User-specific models / model localization work. API exposure ongoing. Branch management and modeling demos. Unnesting data complex aggregation tooling. Snowflake key-pair auth for DB connections. Custom vis library (12 visualization libraries via vibe code). Subtotal visualization polish. Spider/radar chart custom vis. Business growth visualization example.
